                <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8mm; flex:1; min-height:0;">
                  <div>
                    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:42px; margin:0;">
                      Scegli il pacchetto <span>che ti fa crescere</span>
